headline: Dow Jones Futures Fall, Trump Signs Budget Bill Into Law; Tesla Rival Uber Leads 5 Stocks In Buy Zones
summary: President Trump signed his budget bill into law after the stock market hit highs ahead of Independence Day. Tesla fell while Uber broke out.
